NUMBER 509
NAME Woods, grove
MONSTER_GROUP 11
FOREST
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Crude dwellings of branches and rusted metal plates cower behind scabrous
trunks and offer little protection or comfort. The grove exudes dispair like
the corrupt stench from a long unopened tomb. A makeshift bridge leads over
a scum-filled pond.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT D 508
EXIT S 510

ITEM 0 608 VAL2=3261
EXTEND 0 made from planks of rotting wood







NUMBER 3261
NAME Bridge Over Pond
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Secured to a large tree, the bridge bends to the southwest towards an odd
construction site. The stench from the pond below rises to meet you, making
you almost queasy. As you look down, you notice a few kvantars drinking from
the scum-filled waters, apparently not minding the decaying vegetation and
animal life within it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 509
EXIT SW 3262




NUMBER 3262
FOREST
MONSTER_GROUP 109
DAY_LIGHT
NAME Kvantar Construction, Ledge
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
What may someday be a fortress or a tower looms over you here - or perhaps
"leans over you" would be a more appropriate description. You are unable to
determine whether this effect was the architecht's intention, or if the ground
under it simply shifted, but the structure definitely stands at an angle other
than "straight up". A bridge leads over a pond to the northeast.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 3263
ITEM 0 608 VAL2=3261
EXTEND 0 made from planks of rotting wood





NUMBER 3263
NAME Kvantar Construction
INDOOR_FLOOR
MONSTER_GROUP 109
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The interior of this structure has been completed, but unfurnished. Its floors
are bare, save for scattered bones and animal carcasses, and its mirmach walls
are also bare, not counting the fresh blood smeared across it. An occasional
droplet of water falls from the ceiling, rolling down the wall and mixing with
the stains of blood.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 3264
EXIT E 3262




