NUMBER 3265
NAME Construction, Second Floor
INDOOR_FLOOR
MONSTER_GROUP 109
DARKNESS
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Whereas the rooms below were constructed with meticulous care, this area looks
to have been built either in a hurry, or by grossly unskilled carpenters. The
mirmach panels that make up the walls do not match in length or thickness.
Most do not reach the ceiling, allowing thick foliage to creep into the room.
A stairway leads back down.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 3266
; Stairway to Hell
ITEM 0 81 VAL2=3264







NUMBER 3266
NAME Construction, Second Floor
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
MONSTER_GROUP 109
DARKNESS
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The level below is visible through cracks in the warped floorboards, the
result of poor carpentry on the part of the kvantars that built this place and
the fact that the ceiling has not been fully constructed, allowing the
elements to reach this room. A ladder leans against the wall, leading upwards.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 3265
ITEM 0 335 VAl2=3267
IFVERB JUMP -1
        ECHO ALL The floorboards creak beneath your feet.
        AFFECT 3263
        ECHO ALL The ceiling creaks.
        AFFECT 3266
ENDIF






NUMBER 3267
NAME Kvantar Construction, Ladder
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
; Is there a 'ladder' terrain type?
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
Your position atop the kvantar construction affords you a good view of the
surrounding land. To the west is the Eltinmar River, past which you can make
out the Grymwood Forest. Far to the northeast are the Teeth of Shartan, a
chilly mountainous region fabled to be inhabited by elemental giants and
ursines. Past a stretch of grassland to the east is dry, empty wasteland,
while off to the south is the Inner Sea. For a moment, you entertain climbing
further up the ladder, but a quick look tells you that it would be impossible
to do so without falling to the base of the structure.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT D 3266
EXIT U 3262

IFPREVERB U -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You attempt to climb further up the ladder in order to get a better view, but end up slipping and falling...
        ECHO OTHERS %N attemps to climb further up the ladder, but only manages to slip and fall.
        MOVE 3262
        AFFECT 3262
        ECHO ALL %N comes tumbling down from above.
        DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 20 ...you land on some vegetation with a soft thud.
        POSITION LAY
        AFFECT 3267
ENDIF






